"Apple II Interface Card's Drive 2 header or Apple III/III+'s external port. "
"Load disk image into FujiNet's Disk II Drive 1 slot, which is presented to "
"the interface as the sole emulated Disk II. Apple III/III+ requires a 26-pin "
"to 20-pin adapter."
