msgid "Power"
msgstr ""

#: src/users/quickstart/apple.md:140
msgid ""
"FujiNet is powered directly from the Apple II bus -- no external power is "
"required. You can optionally power the FujiNet from the USB port on the "
"board. The USB port is also used for [firmware updates](#updating-firmware) "
"and provides debug output messages to a serial monitor on a computer. The "
"web-based management and WebDAV access to the SD card continue to be "
"accessible if powered from USB while the host Apple II is powered down."
