#: src/users/quickstart/rs232.md:1
msgid "RS-232 (MS-DOS PC) Quickstart Guide"
msgstr ""

#: src/users/quickstart/rs232.md:3
msgid ""
"Welcome to the FujiNet quickstart guide for RS-232 serial connections. "
"FujiNet RS-232 currently targets MS-DOS (PC-compatible) systems via a "
"standard serial port. Support for other serial devices may be added in the "
"future. For a broader overview of all supported platforms, see the [Platform "
"Overview](../platform_overview.md)."
msgstr ""

#: src/users/quickstart/rs232.md:5
msgid ""
"**Beta Notice:** FujiNet RS-232 support is under active development. Some "
"features (notably the on-screen CONFIG application) are not yet fully "
"functional. Join the [FujiNet Discord](https://discord.gg/7MfFTvD) for the "
"latest updates."
msgstr ""

#: src/users/quickstart/rs232.md:9
