msgstr ""

#: src/users/n_device/basic_usage.md:11
msgid "You are in **BASIC** (not the DOS menu)"
msgstr ""

#: src/users/n_device/basic_usage.md:13
msgid ""
"For details on loading the handler, see the [N: Device "
"Overview](overview.md#loading-the-n-device-handler)."
msgstr ""

#: src/users/n_device/basic_usage.md:15
msgid "Loading BASIC Programs"
msgstr ""

#: src/users/n_device/basic_usage.md:17
msgid ""
"The simplest way to use the N: device is to load and run BASIC programs "
"directly from the network."
msgstr ""

#: src/users/n_device/basic_usage.md:19
msgid "Using a Full Devicespec"
msgstr ""

#: src/users/n_device/basic_usage.md:21
msgid ""
"```basic\n"
"RUN \"N:HTTP://ATARI-APPS.IRATA.ONLINE/BLACKJACK.BAS\"\n"
"```"
msgstr ""

#: src/users/n_device/basic_usage.md:25
msgid ""
"This downloads `BLACKJACK.BAS` over HTTP and runs it immediately. BASIC "
"supports devicespecs up to **128 characters** in length, so most URLs will "
"fit without issue."
msgstr ""

#: src/users/n_device/basic_usage.md:27
msgid "Using a Directory Prefix"
msgstr ""

#: src/users/n_device/basic_usage.md:29
msgid ""
"For repeated access to the same server, set a directory prefix first using "
"XIO call 44. This matches the same call used by MyDOS and SpartaDOS and "
"works regardless of which DOS is loaded:"
msgstr ""

#: src/users/n_device/basic_usage.md:31
msgid ""
"```basic\n"
"XIO 44,#1,0,0,\"N:HTTP://ATARI-APPS.IRATA.ONLINE/\"\n"
"RUN \"N:BLACKJACK.BAS\"\n"
"```"
msgstr ""

#: src/users/n_device/basic_usage.md:36
msgid ""
"The prefix `HTTP://ATARI-APPS.IRATA.ONLINE/` is automatically prepended, so "
"`N:BLACKJACK.BAS` resolves to the full URL."
msgstr ""

#: src/users/n_device/basic_usage.md:38
msgid ""
"You can also use the [NCD tool](tools.md#ncd) to set the prefix before "
"entering BASIC."
msgstr ""

#: src/users/n_device/basic_usage.md:40
msgid "Saving BASIC Programs"
msgstr ""

#: src/users/n_device/basic_usage.md:42
msgid ""
"Save programs to network file systems the same way you would save to disk:"
msgstr ""

#: src/users/n_device/basic_usage.md:44
msgid "Direct Save"
msgstr ""

#: src/users/n_device/basic_usage.md:46
msgid ""
"```basic\n"
"SAVE \"N:TNFS://HOMESERVER/PEWPEW.BAS\"\n"
"```"
msgstr ""

#: src/users/n_device/basic_usage.md:50
msgid "Save with Prefix"
