#: src/users/n_device/basic_usage.md:52
msgid ""
"```basic\n"
"XIO 44,#1,0,0,\"N:TNFS://HOMESERVER/\"\n"
"SAVE \"N:PEWPEW.BAS\"\n"
"```"
