#: src/users/bbs/connecting.md:3
msgid ""
"FujiNet's built-in WiFi modem emulation allows your Atari to connect to "
"bulletin board systems (BBSes) over the internet using standard "
"Hayes-compatible AT commands. This guide walks you through connecting to a "
"BBS step by step."
msgstr ""

#: src/users/bbs/connecting.md:7
msgid "An Atari computer with FujiNet connected and powered on"
msgstr ""

#: src/users/bbs/connecting.md:8
msgid "A working WiFi connection configured in [CONFIG](../config/overview.md)"
msgstr ""

#: src/users/bbs/connecting.md:9
msgid ""
