#: src/users/bbs/connecting.md:46
msgid "Once BOBTerm is loaded, press `B` to cycle through baud rates."
msgstr ""

#: src/users/bbs/connecting.md:47
msgid ""
"Press `B` once to select **2400 baud**, or press `B` twice to select **4800 "
"baud**."
