"**FujiNet Control Device** -- adapter configuration, WiFi management, "
"host/device slot operations, clock, app keys, and other system-level "
"functions"
msgstr ""

#: src/developers/programming/atari/overview.md:30
msgid "`$71` - `$78`"
msgstr ""

#: src/developers/programming/atari/overview.md:30
msgid ""
"**N: Network Devices** -- up to eight simultaneous network connections, each "
"supporting protocols such as HTTP, HTTPS, TCP, UDP, FTP, TNFS, SMB, and more"
msgstr ""

#: src/developers/programming/atari/overview.md:32
